1. Ownership

The Software and all original source code, assets, and documentation are
the intellectual property of S44Gaming. S44Gaming retains full copyright
and ownership of the Software at all times.

Modifying this Software does NOT transfer ownership and does NOT remove
or replace the original copyright.

2. Permission for Non-Commercial Use

Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy
of this Software and associated documentation files (the "Software"), to use,
copy, modify, and distribute the Software for NON-COMMERCIAL purposes only,
subject to the following conditions.

3. Attribution Requirement

All copies of the Software, including modified versions or derivative works,
must clearly credit:

"Original Software by S44Gaming"

This attribution must be visible in at least one of the following:

* the repository README
* the documentation
* the software credits
* the license file

You may not claim the Software or any derivative work as your own original work.

4. Redistribution of Modified Versions

If you distribute a modified version of the Software, you MUST:

* Include this license file unchanged
* Clearly state that your version is modified
* Credit S44Gaming as the original author
* Provide a visible changelog describing your modifications

Example notice:

"This project is a modified version of software originally created by S44Gaming."

5. No Rebranding

You may not remove references to S44Gaming or present the Software
as if it were entirely your own creation.

Renaming the project is allowed ONLY if the original author attribution
remains clearly visible.

6. Strict Non-Commercial Restriction

Commercial use of this Software or any modified version is strictly prohibited
without explicit written permission from S44Gaming.

You are strictly prohibited from selling, licensing, sublicensing,
monetizing, or otherwise providing this Software or any derivative work
in exchange for payment, whether directly or indirectly.

You are further prohibited from placing the Software behind any form of
paid access, including but not limited to:

* selling the Software
* charging for access
* monetizing downloads
* paid distribution
* paid mods
* donations required for access
* paywalled versions
* monthly or recurring subscriptions
* membership tiers or supporter programs
* exclusive supporter-only content
* early access provided in exchange for payment, subscription, or donation
* "donate to download" systems or donation-gated downloads

You may not solicit, accept, or receive donations, tips, sponsorships,
or any other form of financial contribution in connection with the
distribution, access, modification, promotion, or availability of this
Software or any derivative work.

This prohibition applies regardless of whether the Software itself is
sold individually or included as part of a broader paid offering.

This restriction explicitly includes, but is not limited to, the use of
this Software on or through:

* Patreon
* Ko-fi
* Buy Me a Coffee
* any digital marketplace
* subscription platforms
* crowdfunding platforms
* any service or platform that provides access in exchange for payment,
  membership, recurring financial support, tips, or donation-gated access.

Even if the Software has been modified, commercial use is NOT allowed
without explicit written permission from S44Gaming.

7. License Preservation

This license and copyright notice must remain included in all copies
or substantial portions of the Software.

Removing or altering this license is not permitted.

8. Disclaimer

THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND,
